<section id="experience" class="section-pad grid-2" style="align-items: center; padding-top: var(--space-2xl); padding-bottom: var(--space-2xl);">
  
  <div style="background-color: var(--color-primary); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: var(--space-lg); position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
    <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 4px; height: 100%; background: var(--color-accent);"></div>
    <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Track Record of Execution</h3>
    <p style="font-size: var(--text-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); color: var(--color-text-main); font-weight: 500;">
      From automated contract analysis to outbound amplification, if it can be codified, we automate it to perfection.
    </p>
    <ul style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-base); padding-left: 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem;">
      <li>Built and deployed cloud-based AI systems serving massive scale operations.</li>
      <li>Programmed AI-assisted contract cost savings software for major agency clients.</li>
      <li>Architected automated personal outreach platforms delivering consistent 300%+ pipeline growth.</li>
      <li>Deep experience leading development teams to design autonomous multi-agent workflows.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div style="padding-left: 0;">
    <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-4xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">Why We Exist</h2>
    <p style="font-size: var(--text-lg); margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
      Administrative friction is the enemy of velocity. We eliminate it entirely.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: var(--text-base);">
      Automate Momentum exists to bridge the massive gap between heavy operational drag and zero-friction execution. We specialize in rapidly deploying custom AI models and autonomous agent networks directly into your existing infrastructure.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: var(--text-base);">
      This allows modern organizations to radically scale their output and margins without linearly scaling their operational headcount.
    </p>
  </div>

</section>
